## What you need to build

You need to collect, store, and display signing metadata for deployable artifacts.

### High-level flow

```text
JFrog Artifactory
   ↓
Artifact Metadata Collector
   ↓
Signing Metadata Collector
   ↓
Normalization / Enrichment Layer
   ↓
Elasticsearch or PostgreSQL
   ↓
Dashboard
Grafana / Kibana
   ↓
Auditor, AppSec, Leadership Reports
```

